features: Neat and Space-saving Installation: The compact outlet mount and custom short USB cord help create a clean and organized setup for your Blink Sync Module 2, eliminating messy wires and saving space.
256GB Flash Drive: Conveniently store, view, share, and download videos from Blink outdoor cameras, high-quality alloy flash drive boasting a generous 256GB capacity and plug-and-play functionality.
Easy and Tool-free Installation: No drilling, screws, or tools are required to install the Blink Sync Module 2. Simply plug it into any open AC outlet, allowing for quick and hassle-free setup.
Flexible and Portable: The mount allows for easy movement of the Blink Sync Module 2 from one location to another, providing flexibility in positioning and convenience in adapting to changing needs.

Secure and Stable Design: Made of high-quality hard plastic with a buckle design, the mount ensures stable and secure placement of the Blink Sync Module 2, protecting it from accidental falls or loosening.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great view from the Alexa or my iPhone
reviews.reviewText: We bought two doorbells and the synch module with a hanger, and this whole system works great with our internet and our Google mesh. Love that I can tell Alexa, Show me the front door, and she shows me who is there while I'm working remote in the back room. So far, so good, and a friend saw them and bought the same setup too because she could see how easy it was to use. Great product so far, loving the ease of install and ease of use. Easier than Arlo, but then again, we did purchase Arlo a few years ago and technology keeps getting better. Time to replace with this Blink camera setup around the property. It stays connected.
